        <h4><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>3 πράγματα να θυμάσαι</h4>
